{"tid":1459361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每一個細路都要學識接受幫助！！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T17:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T17:32:01.000Z","uid":54698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e906b79852e5a1049f33078d218a62ebe0ed664f","tid":1459361,"uid":54698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月夢遊去足全港九新界機場次次都係錢<br />\n個個發夢發到骨瘦如柴日日食包<br />\n修身齊家治國平天下  你食唔飽抖唔夠點幫手保家衛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你估你淨係出一兩次呀？<br />\n呢個係長期戰黎  唔該全世界細路同我好好保護自己身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n車錢    食物    醫藥    衣物    裝備    傾訴    容身之所<br />\n有需要就要出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔準你地一路為香港付出，但連基本需求都唔敢要！<br />\n你幫緊我地   我地幫返你！<br />\n一啲都唔醜   只係等價交換  <br />\n只要有發夢   你地個個都有資格拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔準你地再餓住個肚發夢！！！！"},{"pid":"7db129834d1d25bac3dc9a92728041161933e3fd","tid":1459361,"uid":54698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cda6b2e8548f03ec91447080074eb65cbf108b","tid":1459361,"uid":54698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde3f5f74b3d757393339516509629199134e154","tid":1459361,"uid":54698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f220846f62beb419eec77e8648e94152a5e91251","tid":1459361,"uid":54698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288bd43cd81bdc7219a9f407c0d96816a8068d92","tid":1459361,"uid":54698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score